{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926600/extras/ShowLoop2.gif?t=1728234392\" /><br><br><strong>Neon Sword</strong> is an open world 3rd person top down action roleplay game with elements of business simulation. The none linear story has multiple choices that effect the world around you leading you down many paths; the person you become is shaped by your decisions made within the game.<br><br><u><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time and Setting</h2></strong></u><br>Neon Sword takes place in the fictional Quaid City in the year 2083. The setting takes inspiration from late 70s to early 90s Sci-Fi, Cyberpunk and Synthwave - Neon Lights, Big hair and dodgy moustache...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926600/extras/ShowLoop3.gif?t=1728234392\" /><br><br><u><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2></strong></u><br>Another crime goes unsolved in the city that is the cesspit of humanity! Well, not if you have any say in the matter as you start a personal crusade of revenge. Are you the hunter or the hunted? You will turn Quaid City upside down hosing the streets clean of the human vermin that infest the dark shadows out of the neon glare as you shape the destiny of Quaid City...<br><br>The time has come to wield the <strong>Neon Sword</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926600/extras/ShowLoop5.gif?t=1728234392\" /><br><br><u><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2></strong></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the neon bathed <strong>Quaid City</strong>.<br></li><li>A living breathing city with a diverse population. <br></li><li>Buy real estate and influence the city around you. <br></li><li>Manage your corporation.<br></li><li>Take the fight to them or become one of them. <br></li><li>A deep story where your choice matters. <br></li><li>Save the city or run it into the ground it's your choice.<br></li><li>Gain respect with different Factions or lose it all. <br></li><li>Augment your character with different abilities.<br></li><li>Buy real estate.<br></li><li>Customise your character, vehicle, home and corporation<br></li><li>Mini games</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/926600?t=1728234392","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/926600?t=1728234392","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728234392","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926600/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728234392","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Neon Sword contains strong language, violence, sexual material and the use of illegal drugs."},"demos":[{"appid":2464990,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926600/extras/ShowLoop2.gif?t=1728234392\" /><br><br><strong>Neon Sword</strong> is an open world 3rd person top down action roleplay game with elements of business simulation. The none linear story has multiple choices that effect the world around you leading you down many paths; the person you become is shaped by your decisions made within the game.<br><br><u><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time and Setting</h2></strong></u><br>Neon Sword takes place in the fictional Quaid City in the year 2083. The setting takes inspiration from late 70s to early 90s Sci-Fi, Cyberpunk and Synthwave - Neon Lights, Big hair and dodgy moustache...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926600/extr